    "Property & Casualty is a separate Texas line of authority from Life & Health. Different exam, different products, overlapping market-conduct spine: honesty, fiduciary premiums, fair claims, clean advertising.",
    "Property basics: actual cash value versus replacement cost, named peril versus open peril, deductibles, coinsurance on commercial property, vacancy restrictions, insurable interest at time of loss, subrogation, proximate cause.",
